summary: A realistic "shelter" style home, for those characters who can't afford an inn!
descriptionHtml:
Do you wish to join the College of Winterhold, but lack the magical capacity to gain entry? Do you lack the funds to stay in The Frozen Hearth? Well then this Player "Home" is for you!

Overlooking The Sea of Ghosts, this is a real estate opportunity not to be turned down! Who needs walls when you can wake up to the sun shining through the broken walls and the blizzard like wind blowing through your hair!

UPDATE! I fixed the Bedroll! A bit stupid of me, but I included the "static" object, rather than an actual usable bed! This is fixed now, so you should be able to sleep in the shelter!
author: Lord Daem
